rows.label: qst200216_msg0001
rows.name:
All right, that should do nicely!
Right in time for me to set sail.

rows.label: qst200216_msg0002
rows.name:
Wouldn't want to keep the
client waiting.

rows.label: qst200216_msg0003
rows.name:
Where are you taking this
cargo exactly?

rows.label: qst200216_msg0005
rows.name: Do you know the client personally?

rows.label: qst200216_msg0006
rows.name:
Ships like mine transport all sorts of
different goods from a bunch of clients.

rows.label: qst200216_msg0007
rows.name:
So I'm afraid I don't really know much
about the people I'm working for.

rows.label: qst200216_msg0009
rows.name:
Where are you handing over this
cargo, then?

rows.label: qst200216_msg0010
rows.name:
All I do is unload them at the port.
None of my business what happens
afterwards. Why d'you want to know?

rows.label: qst200216_msg0012
rows.name:
Well then, I'd better get going.
Thanks for your help!
